divs: Sighting DetailsI was driving in my car on the Garden State Parkway at night. I looked out my window and saw a Saturn shaped object in the sky. The ball in the middle was glowing yellow and there was a red ring going around it. I knew they were attached, because they were moving together. The object was slowly hovering forward. I did not see any aliens. It went behind a tree and then it disappeared.
